---
import TemplateLayout from "@/templates/creative-studio/TemplateLayout.astro";
---

<TemplateLayout
  title="About Us | The Creative Collective"
  description="The story, team, and creative philosophy behind The Creative Collective."
  active="about"
  canonicalPath="/templates/creative-studio/about"
>
<main>
<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="relative overflow-hidden pt-24 pb-32 md:pt-40 md:pb-48">
<div class="absolute inset-0 z-0 opacity-10">

</div>
<div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop relative z-10">
<div class="max-w-4xl">
<span class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-secondary-fixed text-on-secondary-fixed font-cs-label-md text-cs-label-md mb-6 uppercase tracking-widest">About Us</span>
<h1 class="font-cs-display-lg text-cs-display-lg-mobile md:text-cs-display-lg mb-8 leading-none">
                        More Than a Studio. <br/>
<span class="vibrant-gradient-text">A Movement.</span>
</h1>
<p class="font-cs-body-lg text-cs-body-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl">
                        We don't just build brands; we ignite them. Our collective is a gathering of minds who believe that "good enough" is the enemy of greatness.
                    </p>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Origin Section (Asymmetric) -->
<section class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-surface-container-low">
<div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-gutter items-center">
<div class="lg:col-span-7 order-2 lg:order-1">
<div class="relative rounded-[24px] overflow-hidden aspect-[16/10] shadow-2xl">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="A gritty but stylish high-contrast black and white photography of a modern basement studio workspace with glowing neon pink and purple accents. The scene is filled with coffee mugs, multiple monitors glowing with creative code and design software, and artistic sketches pinned to the walls. The lighting is moody with dramatic shadows and sharp highlights, reflecting a late-night creative energy." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuC0pYKb0bSLHA-VqYSs7hf1F1rCy9-6-de6X5tqZfmjqyGOMCjqxvNe4rmHXizHeJs_xgPn6fMDOmQr9tKB9II03tYDBX-hYMsXDIrLGLx4XTo8iVb5PssoYy8wU3r3ZVQitpn7j0nmKI4pvqYGgt4-cJBjjg3Y6WdR6HY2BX5ckokES9al_4XkAj2ATr-BWkgooj93TeLXAZQyF8myg2Tgfq5yHJjo1-mS2pw792fqM23y-tSS0EdxZ27Oknnpo2YEkCk3yYO7F4p1"/>
<div class="absolute bottom-6 right-6 bg-white/10 backdrop-blur-md p-6 rounded-xl border border-white/20 text-white max-w-xs">
<span class="font-cs-label-md text-cs-label-md opacity-70">EST. 2018</span>
<p class="mt-2 font-cs-headline-md italic">"It started with a shared screen and a single cup of cold espresso."</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="lg:col-span-5 order-1 lg:order-2 mb-12 lg:mb-0">
<div class="pl-0 lg:pl-12">
<h2 class="font-cs-headline-lg text-cs-headline-lg-mobile md:text-cs-headline-lg mb-6">Our Origin Story</h2>
<p class="font-cs-body-lg text-cs-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-8 leading-relaxed">
<span class="text-primary font-bold">Born in a basement, fueled by caffeine and a refusal to be boring.</span> The Creative Collective wasn't a business plan—it was a reaction to the bland, the safe, and the corporate. 
                            </p>
<p class="font-cs-body-md text-cs-body-md text-on-surface-variant">
                                We realized the world didn't need another agency. It needed a catalyst. We traded stability for a spark, and since then, that spark has turned into a wildfire of innovation across the digital landscape.
                            </p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Values Section (Bento Grid) -->
<section class="py-24 md:py-32">
<div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
<div class="text-center mb-16">
<h2 class="font-cs-headline-lg text-cs-headline-lg-mobile md:text-cs-headline-lg mb-4">The DNA of Our Chaos</h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant font-cs-body-lg">How we maintain the edge without losing the plot.</p>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
<!-- Clarity -->
<div class="gradient-border-card p-10 flex flex-col justify-between h-full hover:translate-y-[-8px] transition-transform duration-500">
<div>
<div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-tertiary-container flex items-center justify-center text-on-tertiary-container mb-8">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl">lightbulb</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-cs-headline-md text-cs-headline-md mb-4">Clarity</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant">Complexity is easy; simplicity is hard. We strip away the noise to find the signal that matters most to your audience.</p>
</div>
<div class="mt-12 text-primary font-bold flex items-center gap-2 group">
                            Explore Method <span class="material-symbols-outlined group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">arrow_forward</span>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Impact -->
<div class="gradient-border-card p-10 flex flex-col justify-between h-full hover:translate-y-[-8px] transition-transform duration-500 bg-surface-container-highest">
<div>
<div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-primary-container flex items-center justify-center text-on-primary-container mb-8">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl">bolt</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-cs-headline-md text-cs-headline-md mb-4">Impact</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant">We don't settle for "likes." We build for legacy. Every pixel and every line of code is measured by the change it creates.</p>
</div>
<div class="mt-12 text-primary font-bold flex items-center gap-2 group">
                            Our Results <span class="material-symbols-outlined group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">arrow_forward</span>
</div>
</div>
<!-- Playfulness -->
<div class="gradient-border-card p-10 flex flex-col justify-between h-full hover:translate-y-[-8px] transition-transform duration-500">
<div>
<div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-secondary-container flex items-center justify-center text-on-secondary-container mb-8">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl">celebration</span>
</div>
<h3 class="font-cs-headline-md text-cs-headline-md mb-4">Playfulness</h3>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant">The best ideas come from play. We maintain a culture of experimentation where the "stupid" questions lead to brilliant answers.</p>
</div>
<div class="mt-12 text-primary font-bold flex items-center gap-2 group">
                            See the Fun <span class="material-symbols-outlined group-hover:translate-x-2 transition-transform">arrow_forward</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Stats Section -->
<section class="py-20 bg-inverse-surface text-inverse-on-surface">
<div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
<div class="grid grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-12 text-center">
<div>
<div class="font-cs-display-lg text-cs-display-lg-mobile md:text-cs-headline-lg text-primary mb-2">200+</div>
<div class="font-cs-label-md text-cs-label-md opacity-70">BRANDS TRANSFORMED</div>
</div>
<div>
<div class="font-cs-display-lg text-cs-display-lg-mobile md:text-cs-headline-lg text-secondary mb-2">15k</div>
<div class="font-cs-label-md text-cs-label-md opacity-70">CUPS OF COFFEE</div>
</div>
<div>
<div class="font-cs-display-lg text-cs-display-lg-mobile md:text-cs-headline-lg text-tertiary-fixed-dim mb-2">42</div>
<div class="font-cs-label-md text-cs-label-md opacity-70">DESIGN AWARDS</div>
</div>
<div>
<div class="font-cs-display-lg text-cs-display-lg-mobile md:text-cs-headline-lg text-primary-fixed-dim mb-2">∞</div>
<div class="font-cs-label-md text-cs-label-md opacity-70">CREATIVE ENERGY</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Team Section -->
<section class="py-24 md:py-32">
<div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop">
<div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-end mb-16 gap-8">
<div class="max-w-2xl">
<h2 class="font-cs-headline-lg text-cs-headline-lg-mobile md:text-cs-headline-lg mb-6">Meet the Creative Rebels</h2>
<p class="text-on-surface-variant font-cs-body-lg">The misfits, the visionaries, and the obsessives behind every pixel.</p>
</div>
<button class="flex items-center gap-4 group">
<span class="font-bold text-lg">Join the Rebellion</span>
<span class="w-12 h-12 rounded-full border-2 border-primary flex items-center justify-center group-hover:bg-primary group-hover:text-white transition-all">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined">add</span>
</span>
</button>
</div>
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
<!-- Rebel 1 -->
<div class="group">
<div class="aspect-[4/5] rounded-[32px] overflow-hidden mb-6 relative">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110" data-alt="A professional and edgy portrait of a woman with vibrant pink hair and modern glasses, wearing a minimalist black turtleneck. She is standing against a clean, white background with a subtle purple-tinted ambient shadow. Her expression is confident and slightly playful. The lighting is soft but directional, highlighting her features with a high-end editorial feel." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBJFPbBdFavc1J-S1uHqZlno2z0lJtBp3Qli0S-D8Lch0HNiGe7ape6cRgXHuB8eSvWRe0_sbQtBT59kkAHfYn_w-KMkxkvkenI8-egqa9-FFTZB8AdsuDAC8yPbiFbDCCdMOnWqehWDB4Qrs_f8anRVVqTT5WLbcMXmzJukWFt2l2iQpYy9bJm8KH28HOXQ8aypPrVvwv-B_Q1icSAfVCowPKGFzjGQ57aWAZ4SBgizVKRP3VO8HBhDlf5-B7sfmB1XkKRGOlCezlP"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary/80 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 flex items-end p-8">
<div class="text-white flex gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined cursor-pointer hover:scale-125 transition-transform">alternate_email</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined cursor-pointer hover:scale-125 transition-transform">public</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<h4 class="font-cs-headline-md text-cs-headline-md">Zoe 'Spark' Chen</h4>
<p class="font-cs-label-md text-primary font-bold mt-1">CHIEF SPARK OFFICER</p>
</div>
<!-- Rebel 2 -->
<div class="group">
<div class="aspect-[4/5] rounded-[32px] overflow-hidden mb-6 relative">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110" data-alt="A portrait of a male creative with a neatly trimmed beard and a beanie, wearing a stylish denim jacket over a white tee. He is looking off-camera with a thoughtful expression. The background is a minimalist studio setting with high-key lighting. The overall aesthetic is modern, clean, and professional, maintaining a cool and creative vibe with subtle purple shadow accents." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDDYLcRyeGzXSx5FZeTEGsUfFyNPG3xUHvsI27cQnZ2AgAb8i8gY6ph4rHJdY9cPPITezqWG5bk35rGbq9irikgoygICTDz_vHiw7bk5wZsREAY6XJURqNgzY1v7ROkawPLkDwPhIuXCghdKPvHUyhldzEJ4mFdNKGrJyDeAj-DXPd3UZvTwOuI4DPKpmKh0rlKYoU8cRvpfVf45kJsRYsOOr9EKP7tOHzK0BQF45otGejGw-snyfX8eQk5rCFzptV3M9UCdBWcp11a"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-secondary/80 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 flex items-end p-8">
<div class="text-white flex gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined cursor-pointer hover:scale-125 transition-transform">alternate_email</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined cursor-pointer hover:scale-125 transition-transform">public</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<h4 class="font-cs-headline-md text-cs-headline-md">Marcus 'Flow' Reed</h4>
<p class="font-cs-label-md text-secondary font-bold mt-1">HEAD OF MOMENTUM</p>
</div>
<!-- Rebel 3 -->
<div class="group">
<div class="aspect-[4/5] rounded-[32px] overflow-hidden mb-6 relative">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110" data-alt="A portrait of a person with short cropped blonde hair, wearing bold geometric earrings and a colorful oversized blazer. The lighting is very bright and modern, creating a clean light-mode aesthetic. They are smiling warmly at the camera. The image quality is high-end digital photography, perfectly suited for a premium creative agency website." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDx1JX0Uhjlw107Xk4wkQ0CZ1umgA8G_ECWhkwqtSqtGBss2yoP7vePQd579-hJDAj-XZU5B80f-pmN9kGye7eBQlskqYxcdYbi5fO8ok5kA1Vjx6OT1QftkqrMt2kIgcFMGTWnRIkO4YMHTIujgXdft2pBEf4dwZI5_75mC1GI59uBgV6uihlKI_zP8yLWSgOmkwNW6bwp2LooK5ItbTVudnmcAacIZJnpbYkVthRSX2HASwzwniXuGtuch9gBNRz-ZyGAegaBbOhu"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-tertiary/80 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 flex items-end p-8">
<div class="text-white flex gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined cursor-pointer hover:scale-125 transition-transform">alternate_email</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined cursor-pointer hover:scale-125 transition-transform">public</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<h4 class="font-cs-headline-md text-cs-headline-md">Sasha 'Chaos' Kim</h4>
<p class="font-cs-label-md text-tertiary font-bold mt-1">DIRECTOR OF DISRUPTION</p>
</div>
<!-- Rebel 4 -->
<div class="group">
<div class="aspect-[4/5] rounded-[32px] overflow-hidden mb-6 relative">
<img class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-110" data-alt="A stylish portrait of a man with curly hair and a colorful patterned shirt, standing in a bright sunlit studio space. He has a creative and approachable aura. The lighting is natural and vibrant, emphasizing a cheerful and high-energy personality. The image captures the essence of a modern digital nomad/creative professional in a professional studio setting." src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBj30sHB8UTumU3BFttwvL8fysgx8medVh7JM1sIzW8TOqjzAOk97VfuEMSZ7lFNrSsViFbdX65g2N9yOoKJnJKqPtT24aZc_1SMHfnJxTSRFcB_Hp1J-GJWKH2FEXLv-7iVrhLpz5q_fWnUsYOCiEcvPNmB68q8S8HyddUDG5HP1VdUA5FpnQqiK1aZbPA6PaaSlZedtm7yeOHcluTXEBs4SQM9USdTOiB54XpRVUsXssBzZ9I7OGFfm9XKQVs9lhY5clgSbk7FK0U"/>
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-primary-fixed-dim/80 to-transparent opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 transition-opacity duration-300 flex items-end p-8">
<div class="text-white flex gap-4">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined cursor-pointer hover:scale-125 transition-transform">alternate_email</span>
<span class="material-symbols-outlined cursor-pointer hover:scale-125 transition-transform">public</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<h4 class="font-cs-headline-md text-cs-headline-md">Leo 'Pixel' Vance</h4>
<p class="font-cs-label-md text-primary-fixed-dim font-bold mt-1">LEAD VISUAL ALCHEMIST</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- CTA Section -->
<section class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-surface-container overflow-hidden">
<div class="max-w-container-max mx-auto px-margin-mobile md:px-margin-desktop text-center relative">
<div class="absolute -top-24 -left-24 w-64 h-64 bg-primary/10 blur-[100px] rounded-full"></div>
<div class="absolute -bottom-24 -right-24 w-64 h-64 bg-secondary/10 blur-[100px] rounded-full"></div>
<h2 class="font-cs-display-lg text-cs-headline-lg-mobile md:text-cs-headline-lg mb-8 relative z-10">Ready to join the movement?</h2>
<p class="font-cs-body-lg text-cs-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto relative z-10">
                    We're always looking for bold brands and brilliant minds. Let's create something that makes people stop scrolling.
                </p>
<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-6 justify-center relative z-10">
<button class="bg-primary text-white font-bold py-4 px-10 rounded-full hover:scale-105 active:scale-95 transition-all custom-shadow">
                        Start Your Project
                    </button>
<button class="bg-transparent border-2 border-primary text-primary font-bold py-4 px-10 rounded-full hover:bg-primary/5 transition-all">
                        View Our Portfolio
                    </button>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</main>

</TemplateLayout>
